Not every feature needs every slice (e.g. skip tools/ if there are no agent tools). Do keep the same spirit: colocate by role, split components into subfolders when a cluster grows, and keep types/schemas/constants out of implementation files as described above.

React Query hooks (strict)

Do not inline React Query query/mutation definitions inside UI components when they represent reusable data behavior.
Each query hook must live in its own file under hooks/ (e.g. use-fetch-_.ts).
Each mutation hook must live in its own file under hooks/ (e.g. use-mutate-_.ts).
One hook file = one primary query or mutation export.
